parameters: ~~~~! Uwah! An extraordinary number of demons ahead--!?

So there are still this many troops left!? There are more
than I imagined!
What shall we do, Master? Shall we force our way through?

Nuuu! Indeed, the enemy numbers are too great! We can't
defeat them all with our combat skills. It's frustrating,
but it's difficult to proceed any further.

GESHISH... As expected, facing such a large number of demons
would make anyone break out in a cold sweat, huh?
Death Spider!? To appear again as a nuisance here...!

KUKUKU! Have you forgotten the humiliation at Fuma Village?
By the great Gyon-sama's orders, I will not let you pass! I
won't allow you to interfere with the Great Eruption ritual!
GROOOH! All four of you, I'll kill you all!!

~~~~! (We can't defeat them all by ourselves! What should we
do...!)
NANAH? Bullets from a gun!? Wh-who are you--!?
I have no obligation to introduce myself to mere insects.
I'm going to break through here!
--!? The magistrate's office! Why are you here!?

Fuu... haa... I thought I wouldn't have a face to show if I
didn't make it in time, but it seems I've barely made it...

Fufu... I endured the pain and rushed here in a basket to
Mount Fuji. I'm here as your strong reinforcement. Sorry for
being late.

We, the elite forces of the shogunate, 20,000 strong--will
now storm into Mount Fuji, which has become the demons'
headquarters.

What are you doing! Don't give them time to regroup!
Annihilate the demons!

Nuuuu!? To come leading such a well-armed large army despite
having the castle tower burned...! I won't let you go to the
lava cave! Everyone, attack--!
The demons are attacking all at once!?

I can't defeat them all with my lightning strike! Shall we
counterattack?

Karin and Yugiri--we will break through the enemy lines and
make a path! You four proceed to the lava cave beyond Mount
Fuji!

Breaking through enemy lines...!? Such a reckless strategy
against so many demons...?

Lord! Are you alright? You shouldn't be able to move with
your injuries?

I am the Shogun, am I not? It would be utterly shameful to
stay under the covers with such wounds. The pain of my
injuries is nothing serious. What's more important is that
Edo was burned and the shogunate's prestige was damaged.
That is the grave matter.

Lord...! (These wounds are not something you can stand with!
Are you prepared to die... coming here...?)

We cannot leave the calamity that might destroy the world to
just the four of you; it would render the existence of us
warriors meaningless. I absolutely refuse to do something so
cruel as to place the fate of this world on the shoulders of
just four people--

History is not made by one person taking a hundred steps
alone. It is woven when ten thousand people each take a step
forward. I will not let you alone take this dangerous
journey.
Leave this place to us and move forward!

We also have a grudge against the demons for killing our
comrades. We won't let you be the only ones to look good.

Yugiri-dono! Please proceed! We Iga ninjas will also exert
our strength to the very end!

Even you who are injured have rushed here from Edo? My
apologies, I thank you!

...! Another earthquake--? The trembling of the earth is
getting stronger and stronger!

We can't afford to waste time! We must stop the eruption
quickly or it will all be for naught! With such timely
reinforcements, we must make use of them! We will leave the
demon army here to them and proceed to Mount Fuji!

Yeah! Understood, Masaki-chan! Yugiri-chan, Momiji-san!
Let's not fight and move deeper in!

Everyone! Do not be daunted even if our opponents are
demons! Raise a whale wave! We shall smash them with all our
might to seize the future for humanity!

--The momentum of the soldiers has pushed back the demon
forces and opened a path!

Leave this place to us. Once we've annihilated the demon
army, we'll follow after you. There's not much time until
Mount Fuji's big eruption, right?

What are you doing! I've cut through the demon army and
cleared the way. Hurry and move forward! Have no worries. Am
I not a general?

My apologies for the delay... I've gathered all the troops
from the neighboring Kant region. You all go ahead and
strike down the enemy's general. I'm counting on you.
